OL,3,C'Groundbreaking' surgery performed on
OL,4,Cgirl born with heart outside body
OL,6,FThis article and video report contains
OL,7,Fan image of Vanellope's heart on the
OL,8,Foutside of her body
OL,10,FA young girl has had groundbreaking
OL,11,Fsurgery in Leicester after she was
OL,12,Fborn with her heart on the outside of
OL,13,Fher body.
OL,15,FVanellope Hope Wilkins, now seven, was
OL,16,Fborn with a condition called Ectopia
OL,17,FCordis - in which the heart is
OL,18,Fabnormally located either partially or
OL,19,Ftotally outside of the chest.
