OL,3,C'Groundbreaking' surgery performed on
OL,4,Cgirl born with heart outside body
OL,6,FDescribed as a 'miracle baby', she was
OL,7,Fdelivered by caesarian section at the
OL,8,Fcity's Glenfield Hospital in November
OL,9,F2017.
OL,11,FShe survived childhood and is thought
OL,12,Fto be the first baby in Britain to
OL,13,Fsurvive the ultra-rare condition.
OL,15,FShe beat eight-million-to-one odds to
OL,16,Fsurvive, spending her first year in
OL,17,Fintensive care before being able to
OL,18,Fleave hospital.
