OL,3,C'Groundbreaking' surgery performed on
OL,4,Cgirl born with heart outside body
OL,6,FSeven years on, Vanellope has
OL,7,Fundergone a groundbreaking operation
OL,8,Fat Leicester's Royal Infirmary to
OL,9,Fprotect her fragile heart - by
OL,10,Freconstructing a protective cage
OL,11,Faround it - using her ribs.
OL,13,FIt has been years in the making, and
OL,14,Fit is the first time it has ever been
OL,15,Fperformed in the UK.
