OL,3,C'Groundbreaking' surgery performed on
OL,4,Cgirl born with heart outside body
OL,6,FConsultant Paediatric Surgeon at
OL,7,FLeicester Children's Hospital, Nitin
OL,8,FPatwardhan, added: "Being able to
OL,9,Fperform a groundbreaking surgery,
OL,10,Fwhich has never been done before in
OL,11,Fthe UK, is important for our patients
OL,12,Fand for the hospital. Our teams do
OL,13,Fincredible work every single day, and
OL,14,Fthis procedure is another example of
OL,15,Fthis.
OL,17,F"Vanellope is a one-of-a-kind case and
OL,18,FI am proud that we have been able to
OL,19,Fwork together to improve her quality
OL,20,Fof life. We wish her a speedy recovery
OL,21,Fand all the best for the future."
