OL,3,C'Groundbreaking' surgery performed on
OL,4,Cgirl born with heart outside body
OL,6,FDuring the operation, Vanellope was
OL,7,Fput onto a heart-lung machine called
OL,8,Fan extracorporeal membrane oxygenation
OL,9,F(ECMO) machine - a medical device that
OL,10,Ftemporarily takes over the functions
OL,11,Fof the heart and lungs.
OL,13,FThe procedure involved a joint team
OL,14,Ffrom the EMCHC and Leicester
OL,15,FChildren's Hospital totalling around
OL,16,F20 people, including anaesthetists,
OL,17,Fsurgeons, operating department
OL,18,Fpractitioners, perfusionists and
OL,19,Ftheatre nurses.
